channel.title: Legato Survey - a chance to win a mangOH red!
channel.description:
Hello mangOH community,
Legato team wants your feedback! By participating in our **[Legato Survey](https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/7HDQDB6)** you will help us improve Legato and to better your development experience on mangOH! Even better, you’ll be entered to win a MangOH Red!
Suvey link: https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/7HDQDB6
Thanks,
